This one lands on off as well, Virat Kohli reads it well and blocks it out.
Fuller and on middle, Virat Kohli blocks it and gets an inside edge towards square leg. Dot.
Fuller and outside off, Virat Kohli lunges and blocks it away.
FOUR! Errs in line and gets punished. Slightly shorter and on off, Axar Patel drills it through mid-wicket for a boundary!
Fuller and outside off, Axar Patel looks to block it but misses.
Bowls it on middle and leg, Axar Patel eases it to the man at mid-wicket for one.
Full and on off, Virat Kohli flicks it straight to the man at square leg.

OUT! TAKEN! An excellent catch by Mominul Haque and Virat Kohli departs for just a run! Full and outside the off stump forcing Kohli to lean forward to play this. He looks to defend it but gets an inside edge off the pads towards short leg and Mominul Haque takes a sharp catch diving to his left. India are in a lot of trouble now as they lose four wickets in quick succession and they still 108 runs to win.
Howout: c Mominul Haque b Mehidy Hasan

Commentary: Fuller and on off, Jaydev Unadkat taps it to covers for one.
Quicker and on off, Jaydev Unadkat defends it solidly.
This one lands on leg, Jaydev Unadkat defends it back towards the bowler.
Another fuller one as this is again defended towards the bowler.
This is around off, Jaydev Unadkat pushes it through the cover region for a single.
Tossed up, full and outside off, turning in. Axar Patel keeps it out.
Slows it up now and pulls the length back as well. Axar Patel looks to block off the back foot but gets an inside edge onto the pads.
Fuller and around off, Jaydev Unadkat blocks it out.
Floated up around off, Jaydev Unadkat pushes it towards cover-point.
Tossed up again and outside off, Jaydev Unadkat strokes it away through covers for a single.
Bowls it on off, Axar Patel lunges and blocks it solidly.
Fuller and on off, Axar Patel taps it to short covers.
This one lands on off as well, Axar Patel punches it to extra covers for a single. He keeps his strike for the next over.
Turning it in from outside off, Axar Patel defends it back towards the bowler.
Another one outside off, Axar Patel defends it with his pads as the ball lobs towards slips. Dot.
Bowls it outside off again, Axar Patel reads it well and lets it go.
Fuller and on off, Axar Patel defends it to the man at mid off.
Goes fuller again, and on off. Axar Patel knocks it to mid off again.
FOUR! Slightly shorter and on off, Axar Patel rocks back and punches it past extra covers for a boundary! That will be STUMPS on Day 3.
Mehidy Hasan starts with a length delivery at the pads, Jaydev Unadkat gets forward to defend, the ball comes off his gloves and falls just short of Litton Das at first slip.
Full on middle by Mehidy Hasan, Jaydev Unadkat rolls his wrist and executes the sweep to perfection. A fumble at short fine leg allows the batters to run two there.

Mehidy Hasan fires this one quicker, full and on middle, Jaydev Unadkat looks to defend this one and gets rapped on the pads. A loud appeal but the umpire shakes his head. Shakib Al Hasan decides to send it upstairs. The UltraEdge shows that it was pad first but on BallTracking it is umpire's call as it was clipping the leg stump and so the onfield decision stands.
SIX! BANG! Full and on off by Mehidy Hasan, Jaydev Unadkat gets down on one knee and slog sweeps this one towards deep mid-wicket. Clears the fence with ease and collects a maximum.
On a length around middle, Jaydev Unadkat sweeps this one down towards square leg for a single.
Length delivery on middle, Axar Patel pushes this one back to the bowler.
Flighted, fuller around off, Jaydev Unadkat gets forward and defends it to cover.
Short and on middle by Shakib Al Hasan, Jaydev Unadkat goes back and punches it to cover for a single.
Leg bye! On a length around leg and turning in, Axar Patel looks to fend this one but the ball comes off his pads towards short fine leg for a single.

OUT! LBW! Shakib Al Hasan strikes in his first over of the day! Shakib Al Hasan bowls this one quicker and touch fuller on off, Jaydev Unadkat goes back to punch this one and pays the price as he gets caught plumb in front of the stumps. After a word with Axar Patel, he decides to review. The UltraEdge shows no bat and it is three reds on BallTracking. Jaydev Unadkat has to depart and India lose their review.
Howout: lbw b Shakib Al Hasan

Commentary: Short and on off by Shakib Al Hasan, Rishabh Pant stays in the crease and clips this one towards deep square leg. Gets off the mark with a single.
Full outside off, Axar Patel plants his foot forward and defends this one to cover for a dot.
Flighted, on a length on middle, Rishabh Pant shimmies down the track and pushes it back to the bowler.
Full around off, Rishabh Pant drives this one towards deep cover for a single.
On a length outside off and turning away, Axar Patel cuts this one to deep cover for a single.
Full and on middle, Rishabh Pant uses his feet and pushes it down to long on for a single.

FOUR! Short and punished by Axar Patel! Short and on middle by Mehidy Hasan, Axar Patel picks the length early and rocks back to pull this one through mid-wicket. Collects a boundary to get into the 30s.
On a length around leg, Axar Patel goes back to defend but the ball keeps low and hits him low on the pads. A loud appeal but it was going down the leg side.
FOUR! Shakib Al Hasan tosses this one on a length around off, Rishabh Pant brings out the reverse sweep and hits this one through short third man for a boundary.
On a length outside off, Rishabh Pant defens this one towards extra cover for a dot.
Quicker and shorter on middle, Rishabh Pant defends this one back to the bowler.
Fullish outside off by Shakib Al Hasan, Rishabh Pant gets inside and sweeps this one towards fine leg and collects a couple of runs.
On a length on off, Rishabh Pant uses his feet to get to the pitch of the ball but the ball comes off his pads and back to the bowler for a dot.
Length delivery on middle, Rishabh Pant can only push this one back to the bowler.
On a length and down the leg side, Axar Patel looks to work this one fine on the leg side but misses. The ball comes off his pads towards short fine leg for a dot.
Touch fuller on middle and turning away, Axar Patel defends this one towards point for a dot.
Full and on middle, Axar Patel gets forward and drives this one down to long off for a single.
Flighted, on a length on middle, Rishabh Pant advances down the track to work it on the leg sid but gets a leading edge towards point for a dot.
Mehidy Hasan fires this one full and on middle, Rishabh Pant defends this one towards cover for a dot.

OUT! LBW! Mehidy Hasan gets the big fish! Mehidy Hasan bowls this one on a length on middle, the ball drifts with the angle and Rishabh Pant ends up playing down the wrong line as he tried to defend. The ball strikes him in front of the stumps and the umpire raises the dreaded finger. Rishabh Pant discusses with Axar Patel and decides not to review and rightly so as the replays show that the ball was crashing into leg stump. 74 runs are still needed with 4 wickets in hand.
Howout: lbw b Mehidy Hasan

Commentary: Slower and short outside off by Shakib Al Hasan, Axar Patel rocks back and cuts this one towards deep backward point for a single.
On a length and angling down the leg side, Shreyas Iyer looks to clip this one but misses.
Full and on middle, Shreyas Iyer drives this one nicely towards deep cover. Gets off the mark with a single.
Fuller on middle, Axar Patel knocks this one towards mid-wicket for a dot.
Full around off, Axar Patel pushes this one down to long on for a single.
Tossed up, full and on middle, Shreyas Iyer looks to defend but the ball comes off the inner part of the bat towards short leg for a dot.
Beauty! Mehidy Hasan bowls this one on a length on off, turns away after pitching and beats Axar Patel on the outside edge as he looked to defend.
Full on middle, Axar Patel defends this one towards cover for a dot.

OUT! TIMBER! Another one bites the dust! Mehidy Hasan bowls this one on a length and drifting into the batter, Axar Patel goes back to work it on the leg side but fails to get any bat on it. The ball comes off his pads and takes the leg stump to send India into more trouble. Axar departs after a fighting knock and Mehidy Hasan picks up a stellar five-wicket haul. 71 runs are still needed for India to win with just 3 wickets in hand.
Howout: b Mehidy Hasan

Commentary: Fuller on middle, Ravichandran Ashwin pushes this one back to the bowler.
Full around off, Ravichandran Ashwin gets forward and defends this one towards silly mid off.

Mehidy Hasan bowls this one on a length outside off, Ravichandran Ashwin looks to work this one on the off side. Mehidy Hasan thinks he heard a noise and wants Shakib Al Hasan to go for a review but the Bangladesh skipper decides not to send it upstairs.
Nicely floated up, full and on middle and leg. Shreyas Iyer makes a bit of room and pushes it to the left of the bowler.
Shorter length around middle, Shreyas Iyer flicks off the back foot and Mominul Haque makes a sharp stop down to his right at short leg.
This is tossed up on the stumps, Shreyas Iyer blocks it out.
Shakib fires it in around off stump, Iyer stays solid in defense.
On a length and around middle, Shreyas Iyer knocks it down to long on and picks up a single.
Nicely drifted in on a nagging length and into middle. This one keeps a bit low and Ravichandran Ashwin does well to block it off the back foot.
A touch shorter and turning in from outside off, Shreyas Iyer punches it towards the vacant short cover region and scampers through for a run.
On a length and around off, a bit of turn and bounce on offer as well. Ashwin defends it down on the deck.
A bit of yes and no but no harm is done. Flatter one around off, Ashwin pushes it out in front of the man at cover and looks for the single but Iyer sends him back and rightly so.
Around off, this is pushed away toward cover for an easy single.
Tossed up on middle, Shreyas Iyer drives it gently towards silly mid on.
Tosses it up again, full and outside off. Shreyas Iyer presses forward and plays it square of the wicket on the off side for one.
Drifted into the stumps and turning away from the right-hander, Iyer plays it late and with soft hands onto the off side.
Flighted delivery, around off and Iyer pushes it toward cover-point.
Bowls it slower and drops it short outside off, Shreyas Iyer rocks back and cuts it toward sweeper cover to turn the strike over.
Floated up, on a length and around middle, Ashwin nudges it out on the leg side.
Bowled with a bit of a round-arm action and angled in very full at the toes, Ravichandran Ashwin blocks it out.
Shakib tries to slide this one into the pads but the ball angles down the leg side.
This is tossed up wide of the off stump, Shreyas Iyer has to reach out for it and pushes it through the cover region for a single.
This is drifted in from around the off stump, Ravichandran Ashwin puts a big stride forward to defend.
Similar to the previous delivery but the length is pulled back ever so slightly, Ashwin manages to keep it out.

DROPPED! Mominul Haque has been sensational at short leg but he has let go of a relatively easy chance. Nicely flighted around middle and leg, Ravichandran Ashwin nudges it to the left of Mominul and it is at a comfortable height as well. Mominul looks to grab it but ends up snatching at it and Mehidy Hasan seems disappointed. How costly will this miss prove to be?

BYE! Wow, how close was that to the leg stump? This is tossed up full and on the pads, Ravichandran Ashwin shuffles right across the off stump and looks to get inside the line of the ball in order to play the paddle sweep. Ashwin misses and the ball misses the leg stumps by a couple of inches before eluding the keeper. They cross for a bye.
Flatter delivery around the pads, Iyer blocks it out.

Swing and a miss! Taijul Islam comes back into the attack and tosses it up on off stump. Ravichandran Ashwin goes for the big heave across the line but the ball turns away sharply and Ashwin is beaten all ends up.
Shorter one around off, Ashwin punches it through cover for a single.
Floated up around off, Iyer pushes it toward cover.
Keeps it around the off stump and Shreyas Iyer just strokes it through the cover region for a run.
This is tossed up, Ravichandran Ashwin looks to come down the pitch and hit his way out of trouble but mistimes it toward mid on.
Quicker and flatter, around middle, Ashwin stays deep in his crease and blocks it out.
Short around off, Shreyas Iyer goes back and pushes this one to mid-wicket.
Tossed up, full on off, Shreyas Iyer gets forward and defends it back to the bowler.
On a length outside off, Shreyas Iyer looks to work this one on the leg side and closes the bat face early. Gets a leading edge that falls short of cover.
On a length outside off, Shreyas Iyer works this fine towards short third man for a single.
Full on middle, Ravichandran Ashwin advances down the track to push this one on the off side but gets an inside edge towards square leg for a single.
Short and outside off, Shreyas Iyer punches this down to long off for a single.
Full on middle by Taijul Islam, Shreyas Iyer defends this one to cover and wants a single but gets sent back by Ravichandran Ashwin.
On a length on middle, Shreyas Iyer knocks this one back to the bowler.
Touch fuller on off, Shreyas Iyer gets forward and plays this one back to the bowler.
Taijul Islam fires this one on a length and at the pads, Shreyas Iyer pushes this one towards mid-wicket for a single.
Short and on off, Ravichandran Ashwin goes back and punches this one towards deep cover for a single.
Flighted, full and on middle by Taijul Islam, Shreyas Iyer defends this one with a straight bat back to the bowler.
On a length around off, Ravichandran Ashwin gets forward and blocks it out to the left of the bowler.
Fuller on off, Ravichandran Ashwin pushes this one back to the bowler.
Short and on middle, turning into the batter, Ravichandran Ashwin goes back and clips this towards deep square leg for a single.
FOUR! Nicely played! Mehidy Hasan floats this one full around off, Shreyas Iyer plants his foot forward  and drives this one against the spin. Gets it past point for a boundary.
On a length on off, Shreyas Iyer taps this one back to the bowler.
Fuller on off, keeps a bit low but Shreyas Iyer is up to the task and defends this one down the wicket.
Full and quicker on middle, Ravichandran Ashwin blocks this one out for a dot.
Short and on off, turning away, Ravichandran Ashwin pushes this one to mid-wicket for a dot.
On a length around off, Ravichandran Ashwin drives this one towards deep cover for a single.
On a length and drifting onto the pads, Shreyas Iyer clips this one on the bounce to Mominul Haque at short leg who makes a good stop.
On a length on middle, Shreyas Iyer knocks this one towards cover for a dot.
Tossed up, full on off, Shreyas Iyer pushes this one back to Shakib Al Hasan.
Full on middle by Mehidy Hasan, Ravichandran Ashwin looks to clip this one but gets an inside edge back onto the pads.
Full outside off and turning in, Ravichandran Ashwin blocks it out on the off side.
Tad short and turning into the batter, Ravichandran Ashwin goes back and pushes it to mid-wicket.
Full on off from round the wicket, Ravichandran Ashwin drives this one to the left of mid-wicket but cannot get it past Zakir Hasan.
Length delivery at the pads, Ravichandran Ashwin clips this one to deep square leg for a single. 50 needed now to win.
On a length around off, Shreyas Iyer pushes this one to mid-wicket for a dot.
Shakib Al Hasan bowls this one on a length and drifting onto the pads, Ravichandran Ashwin goes back and clips this one to the left of deep square leg for a couple of runs.
Tossed up full and on the stumps, Ashwin pushes it out.
Shakib holds it back a touch and bowls it outside off. The ball turns away and Ashwin ends up pushing at it. The ball goes off the outer half and past point as they pick up a single.
FOUR! Up and over! Tossed up around off, Shreyas Iyer comes down the track and lofts it over the fielder at mid off to pick up a crucial boundary.
Flatter delivery around middle, Iyer just defends it out.

FOUR! Drops it a bit short and Shreyas Iyer latches onto it. This is over off stump and Iyer just rocks back before pulling it well in front of mid-wicket for another boundary. India are now 39 runs away.
This is floated up on middle, Ashwin defends it off the front foot.
Flighted delivery, on a nagging length and around off, Ravichandran Ashwin squeezes it out on the off side for a quick single.
FOUR! Poor bowling and Shreyas Iyer is playing a match-winning knock here. Short and wide, slapped away off the back foot through the cover region for a boundary. Nelson comes up for India.
This is attacking the stumps, Iyer blocks it out.
Full and on off stump, Shreyas Iyer blocks it off the front foot.
Flighted, on off stump, kept out by Iyer with ease.
Khaled Ahmed comes on to bowl for the first time in this innings. He starts off with a good-length delivery, seaming away from leg stump. Ravichandran Ashwin awkwardly fends it away.
Goes full now and angles it into the off stump. The ball keeps a bit low and Ashwin gets an inside edge onto the pads as he looks to block.
FOUR! Wrong line and four easy runs for Ravichandran Ashwin. Length ball angling down leg, Ashwin just flicks it away into the fine leg fence.
Hard length around off and middle, Ashwin defends it out.

EDGED AND FOUR! A stroke of luck here for Ravichandran Ashwin but he will take it. Good length in that channel around off, Ashwin looks to drive but gets a thick outside edge that flies inside the diving man at gully and into the fence. Khaled Ahmed cannot believe his luck and India need 26 more runs to win.
Good length, around the top of off, and solidly kept out by Ashwin.
Taijul Islam comes back into the attack and starts with a short one around off. Shreyas Iyer punches it off the back foot and down to wide long off for an easy single.
Flighted delivery, on off stump, Ashwin blocks it off the front foot.
Shorter length, turning away from leg stump, Ashwin watchfully nudges it down toward short mid-wicket.
Tossed up on off stump, Ashwin pushes it out toward silly mid off.

Flatter delivery around off, Ravichandran Ashwin punches it off the back foot and straight into the pads of the man at silly point. The ball almost ricochets onto the stumps and Ashwin was momentarily out of his crease.
On a length and around off, eased away in front of cover-point for a single.
Short and at the batter by Khaled Ahmed, Ravichandran Ashwin stands tall and pulls this one towards deep square leg for a single.
Good-length delivery in the channel outside off, Shreyas Iyer taps this one towards point and takes a single.
Short of a length outside off by Khaled Ahmed, Ravichandran Ashwin punches this one along the ground to the right of deep point and collects a couple of runs.
Full around off, Ravichandran Ashwin gets hurried and can only drive this one to cover for a dot.

On a length on middle, Ravichandran Ashwin looks to defend this one from the crease but the ball keeps low and he somehow manages to get his bat down on time. The ball comes off the bottom part of the bat and goes on the bounce behind the wicket.
Back of a length and angling in on middle, Ravichandran Ashwin defends this one towards point for a dot.
Tossed up, fuller and on middle, Shreyas Iyer looks to drive this one on the off side but gets it from the inner part of the bat back to the bowler.
On a length around off, Shreyas Iyer gets forward and drives it down to long off for a single.
Length delivery outside off, Ravichandran Ashwin leaves it alone.
Tad short on off, Ravichandran Ashwin punches this one towards cover for a dot.

Fuller and on off by Shakib Al Hasan, Ravichandran Ashwin pushes this one towards mid off and sets off for a single. Najmul Hossain Shanto there takes his eyes off the ball as he went down to collect and concedes the second run.
Short and on leg, Ravichandran Ashwin goes back and whips this one uppishly towards deep mid-wicket for a single. India are now 16 runs away.

SIX! Ravichandran Ashwin greets Mehidy Hasan with a maximum! Mehidy Hasan misses his length and bowls this one short and on middle, the ball does not bounce as expected but Ravichandran Ashwin still goes through with the pull. Clears the deep mid-wicket fence and collects a maximum.

On a length around off, Ravichandran Ashwin defends this one from the front foot but gets a thick outside edge that flies past first slip. Litton Das performs the chase as the batters run two in the process.
Fuller on off, Ravichandran Ashwin gets forward and defends this one down the wicket.
On a length on middle, Ravichandran Ashwin defends this one on the leg side.
FOUR! Tossed up, on a length on off by Mehidy Hasan, Ravichandran Ashwin gets to the pitch of the ball and lofts this one over mid off and collects a boundary. Just 4 needed now for India.

FOUR! Ravichandran Ashwin finishes things off for India! Short and on middle by Mehidy Hasan, Ravichandran Ashwin picks the length early and pulls this one right between mid-wicket and mid on. Gets enough bat on it and it goes for a boundary. India win by 3 wickets and win the series 2-0!
